ing: 1 (12 ounce) container frozen whipped topping, thawed
des: "A quick and delicious pie. It's a fluffy, cherry, pineapple, and nut pie, not too sweet and not heavy. In a graham cracker crust."
ins: In a large bowl, combine cherry pie filling, pineapple, sweetened condensed milk, and chopped nuts. Fold in whipped topping until no streaks remain. Spoon into pie crusts. Chill for 1 hour.
